    <stitle>Spanish - Gu&#237;a para Localizaci&#243;n de Fallas del Sistema El&#233;ctrico - 3200, 4200, 4300, 4400,
        7300, 7400, 7500, 8500, 8600 - POWER STEERING PUMP: VICKERS (LUK) V10NF AND V20NF - LUBRICATION/BLEED SYSTEM -
        BLEED SYSTEM
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="drain" graphiccount="0">
        <title>BLEED SYSTEM</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Fill the reservoir to the indicated level and replace cap.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Start engine and idle, turning wheels full left and full right three times. Shut off engine
                and refill to correct level.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Continue operation in step 2 until correct level is attained.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Run engine at faster RPM and continue to turn wheels back and forth slowly for approximately
                5 minutes. Again refill reservoir to the correct level.
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
